-- European Soccer Championship to Be Played Across Region in 2020
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-12-06T16:26:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-06/european-soccer-championship-to-be-played-across-region-in-2020.html
The 2020 European soccer championship
will be played in multiple countries across the region,
continental governing body UEFA said at a press conference
today.  France  will host the next European tournament in 2016.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  